shopicruit_2016
by Carlos Campana

Solution to Shopify Fall Intern 2016 challenge

date:
    June 2016

description:
    Solution to Shopify Fall Intern 2016 challenge

require::

    python2.6 or later
    numpy
    jsonschema
    urllib3

install::

    % python setup.py build
    % python setup.py install

usage::

    >>> import shopicruit_2016
    >>> # When input is a real number the package assumes input == budget 
    >>> input_value = 169.13 
    >>> total_grams = shopicruit_2016.report_for_Alice(input_value)
    >>>
    >>> # When input is an integer number the package assumes input == number
    >>> # of computer/keyboard variants
    >>> input_value = 23
    >>> total_grams = shopicruit_2016.report_for_Alice(input_value)

